# FavourIgnoreOverLetWild (FL0055)

## Cause

A value is binded to a wildcard e.g. `let _ = Console.ReadLine()`.

## Rationale

Using the ignore function makes it clear what is intended to happen, rather than something that may be a mistake.

## How To Fix

